perfect and he's hugging his Springer right now!\n\nWestminster is just around the corner and I am sure \"James\" will be the\ncenter of attention as the reining Best in Show dog.\n\n \n\nI have some exciting news, I have a Champion Sheltie named \"Jamie\"  that\nI am bringing to show at Westminster this year.\n\nI am thrilled.  This will be my first time back to the Garden since my\nbeloved Mocha died.\n\n \n\nI have a big favor to ask.  I have searched for hotels and during those\ndays of Westminster, everyone I tried is booked solid.  A few years ago\nI stayed in one of Jeffrey's apartments in the City.  Would you be so\nkind as to ask him if I and my entourage  (handler and girl friends)\ncould use his places again?  \n\nGee, maybe he would like us to stay with him!!!  He'd have a great time\nwith us, doggie and all!!\n\n \n\nTell him too, that the Quarter Horse Congress is in full swing.  He\nshould come and go with me as he did in the old days.\n\n \n\nI have so many really cool things to tell him about.   What's the best,\non the phone or should I send him a note?\n\n \n\nThanks a million Lesley!\n\nPamela\n\n\n\n\n\n________________________________\n\nSee what's new at AOL.com <http://www.aol.com?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001170>\nand Make AOL Your Homepage\n<http://www.aol.com/mksplash.adp?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001169> .\n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n<style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n @font-face\n\t{font-family:Calibri;\n\tpanose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\n@font-face\n\t{font-family:Tahoma;\n\tpanose-1:2 11 6 4 3 5 4 4 2 4;}\n /* Style Definitions */\n p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{margin:0in;\n\tmargin-bottom:.0001pt;\n\tfont-size:12.0pt;\n\tfont-family:\"Times New Roman\",\"serif\";}\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\n\t{mso-style-priority:99;\n\tcolor:blue;\n\ttext-decoration:underline;}\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\n\t{mso-style-priority:99;\n\tcolor:purple;\n\ttext-decoration:underline;}\nspan.EmailStyle17\n\t{mso-style-type:personal-reply;\n\tfont-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\";\n\tcolor:#1F497D;}\n.MsoChpDefault\n\t{mso-style-type:export-only;\n\tfont-size:10.0pt;}\n@page Section1\n\t{size:8.5in 11.0in;\n\tmargin:1.0in 1.0in 1.0in 1.0in;}\ndiv.Section1\n\t{page:Section1;}\n-->\n</style>\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <o:shapedefaults v:ext=\"edit\" spidmax=\"1026\" />\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\n <o:shapelayout v:ext=\"edit\">\n  <o:idmap v:ext=\"edit\" data=\"1\" />\n </o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]-->\n</head>\n\n<body lang=EN-US link=blue vlink=purple id=\"role_body\">\n\n<div class=Section1>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:#1F497D'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\"Calibri\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:#1F497D'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<div style='border:none;border-top:solid #B5C4DF 1.0pt;padding:3.0pt 0in 0in 0in'>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\"'>From:</span></b><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Tahoma\",\"sans-serif\"'> Noital4u@aol.com\n[mailto:Noital4u@aol.com] <br>\n<b>Sent:</b> Wednesday, October 03, 2007 8:48 AM<br>\n<b>To:</b> Lesley Groff<br>\n<b>Subject:</b> Westminster<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Good morning Lesley,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Tell me how things worked out with Jeffrey's puppy???&nbsp; I hope\neverything was perfect and he's hugging his Springer right now!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Westminster is&nbsp;just around the corner and I am sure\n&quot;James&quot; will be the center of attention as the reining Best in Show\ndog.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>I have some exciting news, I have a Champion Sheltie&nbsp;named\n&quot;Jamie&quot; &nbsp;that I am bringing to show at&nbsp;Westminster this\nyear.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>I am thrilled.&nbsp; This will be my first time back to the Garden\nsince my beloved Mocha died.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>I have a big favor to ask.&nbsp; I have searched for hotels and\nduring those days of Westminster, everyone I tried is booked solid.&nbsp; A few\nyears ago I stayed in one of Jeffrey's apartments in the City.&nbsp; Would you\nbe so kind as to ask him if I and my entourage&nbsp; (handler and girl friends)&nbsp;\ncould use his places again?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Gee, maybe he would like us to stay with him!!!&nbsp; He'd have a\ngreat time with us, doggie and all!!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Tell him too, that the Quarter Horse Congress is in full\nswing.&nbsp; He should come and go with me&nbsp;as he did in&nbsp;the old days.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>I have so many really cool things to tell him about.&nbsp;&nbsp;\nWhat's the best, on the phone or should I send him a note?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Thanks a million Lesley!<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Pamela<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:12.0pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><br>\n<br>\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<div class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:7.5pt;text-align:center'><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>\n\n<hr size=2 width=\"100%\" align=center>\n\n</span></div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.5pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>See what's new at <a\nhref=\"http://www.aol.com?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001170\" target=\"_blank\"\ntitle=\"http://www.aol.com?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001170\">AOL.com</a> and <a\nhref=\"http://www.aol.com/mksplash.adp?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001169\" target=\"_blank\"\ntitle=\"http://www.aol.com/mksplash.adp?NCID=AOLCMP00300000001169\">Make AOL Your\nHomepage</a>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":0,"avatar_color":"#0f9d58","stars":5,"is_redacted":false}]